---
import ToolPage from '../layouts/ToolPage.astro';
---
<ToolPage
  title="Document Lens"
  titleHtml='Document <span class="brand-mark">Lens</span>'
  tagline="Batch-analyse large PDF collections with pre-built research frameworks, n-gram discovery, and shareable project bundles."
  description="Batch PDF analysis for researchers — keyword frameworks, n-gram discovery, and rich visualisations on your desktop."
  brand="document-lens"
  repo="michael-borck/document-lens"
>

<section class="app-section">
  <h2>What it does</h2>
  <div class="app-features">
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Batch PDF import</h3>
      <p>Drop in annual reports, research papers, contracts — whole collections at once — and run analysis across the set.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Research frameworks</h3>
      <p>32+ pre-built keyword frameworks across sustainability, cybersecurity, finance, healthcare, legal, academic, and PM domains.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Hierarchical taxonomies</h3>
      <p>Organise keywords into multi-level tiers (e.g. SDG Pillar &gt; Goal &gt; Keyword) and aggregate coverage at any level.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>N-gram discovery</h3>
      <p>Surface frequently occurring bigrams and trigrams to find terminology patterns you didn't know to search for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Rich visualisations</h3>
      <p>Word clouds, heatmaps, treemaps, and trend charts to compare coverage across documents and frameworks.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-feature">
      <h3>Share &amp; export</h3>
      <p>Export to CSV, Excel, or JSON — or package everything into a <code>.lens</code> bundle to share with collaborators.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="app-section">
  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <div class="app-steps">
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Import &amp; analyse</h3>
      <p>Bring in a folder of PDFs and run document-level analysis — readability, writing quality, word frequency.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Pick a framework</h3>
      <p>Choose a pre-loaded keyword framework for your domain, or drop in your own custom keyword list or taxonomy.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Search &amp; discover</h3>
      <p>Run keyword searches with tier-level aggregation, and let n-gram discovery surface the terms that actually matter.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="app-step">
      <h3>Visualise &amp; share</h3>
      <p>Generate charts comparing coverage and trends, then export results or bundle the whole project for collaborators.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</ToolPage>
